data.description: Flexible owner financing offered!   Discover the perfect blend of space and style in this magnificent two-story home, boasting 5 bedrooms and 2.5 baths across an expansive 2555 square feet of living space. As you enter, be greeted by an impressive open-to-above entryway that leads to a convenient powder bath and unfolds into a spacious living area, creating an inviting atmosphere from the moment you step inside.  The heart of this home is the open concept eat-in kitchen, seamlessly integrating with the living area. The kitchen is perfect for culinary explorations and casual dining, while the separate dining area provides an ideal setting for more formal occasions. This space extends effortlessly to an outdoor patio, setting the stage for memorable entertaining and relaxation under the sky. The second floor is thoughtfully designed with a focus on comfort and elegance. It features the master suite, a haven of tranquility, offering a cozy sitting area, a well-appointed master bath, and a large walk-in closet, ensuring a private and luxurious living experience. Upstairs has welcoming loft. This versatile space can serve as a family room, a play area, or a quiet retreat, adapting to your lifestyle needs. This home is a harmonious blend of comfort, style, and functionality, designed to accommodate a variety of living situations and preferences. It's not just a house; it's a place where life's moments are to be cherished.This version aims to evoke a sense of warmth and homeliness, emphasizing the functional and aesthetic aspects of the property. Feel free to adjust any details to better match the specifics of the home.
